    <!--Specify a theme with its name and mode here
       "title" is the name of the theme displayed to the user
       "mode" is the mode of the theme it can either the "Dark" or "Light".
       "preview" is the preview image shown to the user when selecting themes.
       "wallpaper" is an optional wallpaper provided along the theme.
